      "acceptanceCriteria": "Linear elastic titanium alloy constitutive model with nonlinear contact at screw-rod and rod-block interfaces; geometric nonlinearity enabled. Justified by material behavior within yield for majority of loading range.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V modeled as linear elastic (E=114 GPa, ν=0.34) consistent with ASTM F1472 material properties. Contact interfaces employ augmented Lagrangian formulation. Geometric nonlinearity (NLGEOM) enabled to capture large-displacement bending. Model form appropriate for pre-yield and near-yield compression-bending regime. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
