      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production hardware. Dimensional inspection and material certification completed for each specimen. Constructs split across two independent test laboratories (Lab A: n=6, Lab B: n=5) to assess inter-laboratory variability. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
