      "acceptanceCriteria": "Multiple test conditions (loading rates, environmental conditions) required at level 3; single ASTM F1717 standard condition tested.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 standard condition (quasi-static, ambient, 10 mm/min crosshead speed). No variation in loading rate or environmental conditions was explored. This limits the factor to achieved level 2, which is below the required level 3. Noted as a known gap; impact assessed as low given the deterministic nature of the comparison and consistency with regulatory precedent for this device class."
    },
    {
