      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 fixture geometry (block spacing 44 mm, vertebral body block dimensions) reproduced in FEA. Loading fixture compliance measured experimentally and subtracted from raw load-displacement data prior to QoI extraction. Correspondence between test and model boundary conditions confirmed by overlay of fixture CAD with FEA assembly. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
