      "rationale": "Stiffness: FEA 312 N/mm vs. experimental mean 308 N/mm (1.3% difference, E/uval=0.41). Yield force: FEA 1840 N vs. experimental mean 1795 N (2.5% difference, E/uval=0.78). Force at 40 mm: FEA 2210 N vs. experimental mean 2185 N (1.1% difference, E/uval=0.33). All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
