      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three standard ASTM F1717 output metrics used in FDA 510(k) submissions for pedicle screw systems. These QoIs directly characterize structural integrity and fatigue risk relevant to the COU. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
